---
import "./Bath.css";
---
<section class="remodel-bath">
    <h2 class="remodel-bath__title">What’s Included in a Full Bathroom Remodel?</h2>
    <div class="remodel-bath__grid">
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">CUSTOM VANITY INSTALLATION</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Elegant and functional vanities designed to fit your space, with personalized sink and storage options to match your lifestyle.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">FLOORING REPLACEMENT</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Durable, waterproof flooring options including tile, luxury vinyl plank (LVP), and engineered wood for a clean and lasting finish.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">TILE INSTALLATION</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    High-end tile installation for floors, showers, and backsplashes — available in a wide range of textures, colors, and patterns.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">WALL FINISHES & PAINTING</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Moisture-resistant paints and refined wall textures for a sleek, polished look that elevates your entire space.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">SHOWER & BATHTUB UPGRADES</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Modern walk-in showers, frameless glass enclosures, freestanding tubs, or tub-to-shower conversions to suit your vision.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">ACCESSIBILITY UPGRADES</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Install grab bars, curbless showers, wider doorways, and ADA-compliant solutions for enhanced safety and ease of use.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">LIGHTING & VENTILATION</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Layered lighting systems and exhaust fans to enhance visibility, comfort, and ambiance with designer fixtures.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">STORAGE SOLUTIONS</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Built-in cabinetry, recessed shelves, and custom-designed niches to reduce clutter and improve organization.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">PLUMBING & FIXTURES</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Upgrade or reroute plumbing lines to accommodate new sinks, showers, bathtubs, and toilets with precision installation.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="remodel-bath__item">
            <span class="remodel-bath__icon">✔️</span>
            <div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-title">FINAL CLEANING & WALKTHROUGH</div>
                <div class="remodel-bath__item-desc">
                    Thorough post-construction cleaning and a detailed final inspection to ensure everything is perfect before we hand it over.
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>